project_descr: The objective of the project is to  enhance climate resilience of ecosystems through Assisted Natural Regeneration (ANR), Agroforestry and Integrated Fire Management and enhancing energy and resource use efficiency.

outputs.output_descr: Reducing the vulnerability of local communities to the effects of climate change by enhancing the capacity of Forest Department and local communities to plan for climate change and implementing adaptation measures.

project_title: promoting communit based climate resilient forest regen
